edu.caltech.nanodb.server

Class NanoDBServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.caltech.nanodb.server.NanoDBServer

  • public class NanoDBServer
extends Object
    This class provides the entry-point operations for managing the database server, and executing commands against it. While it is certainly possible to implement these operations outside of this class, these implementations are strongly recommended since they include all necessary steps.
